extends layout

block content-head
  title About Us - LMS
  style.
    .about-content {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .about-content h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .about-content p {
      color: #34495e;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

block content-body
  section.intro
    h1 About Us
    p Learn more about our mission and values.

  section.about-content
    h2 Our Story
    p Founded in 2024, our Learning Management System (LMS) was born out of a passion for education and a desire to make quality learning accessible to everyone. We believe that knowledge is power, and our platform is designed to empower learners from all walks of life.
    
    h2 Our Mission
    p Our mission is to provide a comprehensive, user-friendly platform that connects learners with high-quality educational content. We strive to create an environment that fosters growth, curiosity, and lifelong learning.
    
    h2 Our Team
    p We are a diverse team of educators, technologists, and lifelong learners. Our combined expertise allows us to create a platform that not only meets the needs of today's learners but also anticipates the educational challenges of tomorrow.
